---
title: Spicy Beef Curry with almond flaked pilau
description: This fiery curry is for all the heat lovers out there. Try it if you dare! Fragrant pilau rice and fresh coriander provide a balancing element with added crunch from lightly toasted almonds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R20_W46_IE_IECB14323-3_edit_rice__Main_2high-2f15ae7f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/64dc86bd4b03281706cdd39e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/spicy-beef-curry-64dc86bd4b03281706cdd39e
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Indian
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
